export const categories = {

    { id: 15, name: "Socks", image: "socks.png", price: "$5", category: "Clothing", description: "Soft and breathable socks for all-day comfort." },

    { id: 18, name: "Dryer", image: "dryer.png", price: "$250", category: "Home Appliances", description: "High-speed clothes dryer with heat control settings." },
    { id: 19, name: "Washing Machine", image: "washing-machine.png", price: "$850", category: "Home Appliances", description: "Front-load washing machine with smart controls and energy efficiency." }
